name: A World of Ink and Chaos

metadata.name: A World of Ink and Chaos
metadata.description:
If you look beyond what's seen, 
A hidden world of Ink will gleam, 
Where creatures live and beauty thrives, 
And nature reigns with its many lives

Slimy snakes slither through the night,  
Flowers bloom in endless light, 
A world of shadows and mysterious hue,  
Where secrets hide and dreams come true

Their world is so dark and busy, 
But they don't seem to mind, 
As they bask in the moonlight, 
Of a world they've left behind
